## 3. Watchdog ヘルスチェック・復旧フロー

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([main 起動]) --> Mutex{Named Mutex<br/>取得できた?}
    Mutex -->|No| Exit1([既に起動中 → 終了])
    Mutex -->|Yes| Mode{--once<br/>フラグ?}
    Mode -->|Yes| Once[ensure_healthy 1回実行]
    Once --> OnceOK{成功?}
    OnceOK -->|Yes| Exit2([正常終了])
    OnceOK -->|No| Exit3([exit code 1])
    Mode -->|No| Loop[10秒ごとのループ]

    Loop --> HC[is_healthy 呼び出し]
    HC --> StatusCmd["espanso service status<br/>(5秒タイムアウト)"]
    StatusCmd --> CheckRunning{stdout に<br/>'espanso is running'<br/>含む?}
    CheckRunning -->|No| Unhealthy
    CheckRunning -->|Yes| ProcCount["プロセス数カウント<br/>(sysinfo)"]
    ProcCount --> CheckProc{"≥ 3プロセス?"}
    CheckProc -->|No| Unhealthy
    CheckProc -->|Yes| LogCheck["espanso.log 末尾256KB読取"]
    LogCheck --> CritLine{"直近2分以内に<br/>[ERROR] could not<br/>restart worker?"}
    CritLine -->|No| Healthy([Healthy ✓ → ログ出力])
    CritLine -->|Yes, 新規| Unhealthy
    CritLine -->|Yes, 既知| Healthy

    Unhealthy[Unhealthy 検出] --> Retry["復旧リトライ<br/>(最大3回)"]
    Retry --> Kill["全 espanso プロセス kill"]
    Kill --> Wait1[1秒待機]
    Wait1 --> StartCmd["espanso service start --unmanaged<br/>(10秒タイムアウト)"]
    StartCmd --> Wait2[2秒待機]
    Wait2 --> ReCheck{再チェック<br/>is_healthy?}
    ReCheck -->|Yes| Recovered([復旧成功 ✓])
    ReCheck -->|No| RetryLeft{リトライ<br/>残り?}
    RetryLeft -->|Yes| Kill
    RetryLeft -->|No| Failed([復旧失敗 ✗])

    Healthy --> Sleep[sleep 10秒]
    Recovered --> Sleep
    Failed --> Sleep
    Sleep --> HC

    style Healthy fill:#2e7d32,color:#fff
    style Recovered fill:#2e7d32,color:#fff
    style Unhealthy fill:#c62828,color:#fff
    style Failed fill:#c62828,color:#fff
```

