## 5. Watchdog 内部モジュール構成

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class main {
        +main()
        panic_hook 設定
        Named Mutex 取得
        --once / monitor モード分岐
    }

    class HealthState {
        -last_critical_log_line: Option~String~
        -sys: System
        -espanso_cli: String
        +new() HealthState
        +is_healthy() (bool, String)
        +ensure_healthy() bool
    }

    class WinMutex {
        -handle: HANDLE
        +try_acquire(name: &str) Option~WinMutex~
        +drop()
    }

    class CommandResult {
        +completed: bool
        +timed_out: bool
        +exit_code: Option~i32~
        +stdout: String
        +stderr: String
        +error_message: String
        +failed(msg) CommandResult
        +timed_out_result(out, err) CommandResult
        +completed_result(code, out, err) CommandResult
    }

    class Functions {
        +app_dir() PathBuf
        +log_path() PathBuf
        +espanso_log_path() PathBuf
        +resolve_espanso_cli_path() String
        +log(message)
        +trim_for_log(text, max) String
        +kill_process_tree(pid)
        +run_command(file, args, timeout) CommandResult
        +format_command_result(result) String
        +get_espanso_process_count(sys) usize
        +kill_espanso_processes(sys) u32
        +read_tail_text(path, max_bytes) String
        +is_recent_espanso_log_line(line) bool
        +is_critical_espanso_log_line(line) bool
        +get_latest_critical_espanso_log_line() Option~String~
    }

    main --> HealthState : 生成・ループ実行
    main --> WinMutex : 多重起動防止
    HealthState --> Functions : 各種関数呼び出し
    HealthState --> CommandResult : espanso CLI 実行結果
    Functions --> CommandResult : run_command 戻り値

    note for HealthState "10秒間隔で is_healthy → ensure_healthy\nunhealthy時は最大3回リトライ復旧"
    note for WinMutex "Windows Named Mutex (FFI)\nLocal\\EspansoWatchdogMutex"
```

## 6. disable-keybindings ツール

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Input["VSCode default<br/>keybindings.json<br/>(コメント・trailing comma 含む)"]
    -->|引数: input.json| Tool["disable-keybindings.exe"]
    Tool -->|Step 1| Strip["// コメント除去"]
    Strip -->|Step 2| Comma["trailing comma 除去"]
    Comma -->|Step 3| Parse["JSON パース<br/>Vec&lt;InputEntry&gt;"]
    Parse -->|Step 4| Filter["既に - 付きの<br/>コマンドを除外"]
    Filter -->|Step 5| Prefix["command に<br/>'-' プレフィックス付与"]
    Prefix -->|Step 6| Output["出力 JSON<br/>Vec&lt;OutputEntry&gt;"]
    Output -->|"-o output.json"| File["ファイル出力"]
    Output -->|引数なし| Stdout["stdout 出力"]

